data.description: Come and see this beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home featuring an amazing open floor plan. The kitchen features an island that has plenty of storage, pendant lighting above, matching stainless steel appliances, beautiful cabinets, recessed lighting, tiled Travertine backsplash, & granite tiled countertops! 20x20 inch tiled flooring throughout main living areas. New dishwasher & brand new carpet installed in Primary bedroom & guest bedroom in 2022. Enjoy generously sized bedrooms with plenty of closet space. There is a big backyard with a covered patio & plenty of space to entertain. This home has Green features with a rain water harvesting system & leased solar panels with FIXED payments at a low affordable price! You will see a huge savings on your Electric bill! Excellent location near a lot of what Tucson has to offer including the University of Arizona, Banner Hospital, Restaurant's, shopping, and more! Make it your home sweet home!
